OL,3,CTeachers consider 4% pay increase offer
OL,5,FTeachers are considering an offer of a
OL,6,F4% pay increase.
OL,8,FThe formal offer from management for
OL,9,Fthe 2025/26 academic year includes a
OL,10,F4% consolidated increase to all
OL,11,Fteacher salary scale points.
OL,13,FIt also includes a 4% rise to all
OL,14,Fallowances effective from September 1
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FThe offer was described by management
OL,18,Fas one that "reflects our ongoing
OL,19,Fcommitment to ensuring fair and
OL,20,Fcompetitive remuneration for teachers
OL,21,Fin Northern Ireland".
