OL,3,CTeachers consider 4% pay increase offer
OL,5,F"We very much value the vital role of
OL,6,Fteachers and believe this pay award
OL,7,Frepresents the best that can be
OL,8,Fachieved against the backdrop of
OL,9,Fincreasing financial pressures," they
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers Council
OL,13,F(NITC), which represents the five main
OL,14,Fteacher unions, said teachers had
OL,15,Fhoped for more but believe this offer
OL,16,Fis the maximum that is currently
OL,17,Fpossible.
