OL,3,CTeachers consider 4% pay increase offer
OL,5,FIt comes after Education Minister Paul
OL,6,FGivan was given approval by the
OL,7,FStormont Executive to overspend his
OL,8,Fbudget last month to allow the pay
OL,9,Fnegotiations to take place.
OL,11,FHis department is facing a projected
OL,12,Fdeficit of around #267 million for
OL,13,Fthis financial year.
OL,15,FThe NITC welcomed the pay offer in a
OL,16,Fstatement on Tuesday.
