OL,5,F"Each union will now communicate with
OL,6,Ftheir members on how they will consult
OL,7,Fon the offer."
OL,9,FThe National Association of
OL,10,FSchoolmasters/Union of Women Teachers
OL,11,F(NASUWT) said it is recommending its
OL,12,Fmembers accept the offer.
OL,14,FMatt Wrack, general secretary of the
OL,15,FNASUWT, said: "The union commends the
OL,16,Fnegotiating team for delivering this
OL,17,Foffer from management side in what are
OL,18,Fvery difficult circumstances for the
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland Executive.
