OL,3,CTeachers consider 4% pay increase offer
OL,5,F"This offer matches the 4% award made
OL,6,Fto teachers in England for the 2025/26
OL,7,Facademic year and keeps teachers'
OL,8,Fsalaries broadly in line between
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and England. Very
OL,10,Fimportantly there are no strings
OL,11,Fattached to this offer."
OL,13,FJustin McCamphill, NASUWT national
OL,14,Fofficial for Northern Ireland, added:
OL,15,F"We welcome this pay offer, which is a
OL,16,Fsignificant and hard-won achievement
OL,17,Fwhich was only made possible by
OL,18,FExecutive agreement after a
OL,19,FMinisterial Direction.
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@XO]wD@AOU
