OL,5,F"On the basis that there is no
OL,6,Fprospect of additional funding, the
OL,7,Funion will be recommending that
OL,8,Fmembers accept this offer.
OL,10,F"Crucially, this offer is not
OL,11,Fconditional. It allows us to separate
OL,12,Fthe vital issue of pay from our
OL,13,Fongoing campaign to tackle excessive
OL,14,Fteacher workload, for which the
OL,15,FIndependent Panel's report now
OL,16,Fprovides a concrete basis for
OL,17,Fresolution. The minister must now act
OL,18,Fdecisively on those recommendations."
