OL,5,FMarty Lavery, chairperson of the Irish
OL,6,FNational Teachers' Organisation (INTO)
OL,7,Fnorthern committee, said the above-
OL,8,Finflation offer "represents another
OL,9,Fstep towards pay restoration which
OL,10,FINTO has been calling for over the
OL,11,Fpast decade".
OL,13,F"INTO will now consult with our
OL,14,Fmembers before formally responding to
OL,15,Fthis offer," he said.
